OL,3,C'The ocean is overflowing': UN chief
OL,4,Cissues warning about Pacific sea level
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FThe United Nations chief has warned of
OL,8,Fthe peril faced by islands in the
OL,9,FPacific Ocean, as sea levels have
OL,10,Frisen almost twice the global average
OL,11,Fin the past 30 years.
OL,13,FMaking a speech from the island nation
OL,14,Fof Tonga, UN Secretary-General Antonio
OL,15,FGuterres issued a 'Save our Seas' plea
OL,16,Ffor the world to increase support for
OL,17,Fcountries endangered by the climate
OL,18,Fcrisis.
