OL,3,C'The ocean is overflowing': UN chief
OL,4,Cissues warning about Pacific sea level
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"The ocean is overflowing," Guterres
OL,8,Fsaid. "This is a crazy situation:
OL,9,FRising seas are a crisis entirely of
OL,10,Fhumanity's making.
OL,12,F"A crisis that will soon swell to an
OL,13,Falmost unimaginable scale, with no
OL,14,Flifeboat to take us back to safety."
OL,16,FThe Pacific Islands are being hit
OL,17,Fharder than most, suffering a triple
OL,18,Fblow of ocean heating, sea level rise
OL,19,Fand acidification.
