OL,7,FThe effects are harming ecosystems,
OL,8,Fdamaging crops, contaminating fresh
OL,9,Fwater sources, and destroying
OL,10,Flivelihoods.
OL,12,FWorsening floods and tropical storms
OL,13,Fare already devastating the islands.
OL,14,FThe report said that in 2023, 34
OL,15,Fmostly storm or flood-related
OL,16,F"hydrometeorological hazard events"
OL,17,Fled to more than 200 deaths and
OL,18,Faffected 25 million people in the
OL,19,Fregion.
