OL,3,C'The ocean is overflowing': UN chief
OL,4,Cissues warning about Pacific sea level
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FIn a second report published Tuesday,
OL,8,Fthe UN's climate action team said the
OL,9,Fclimate crisis and sea level rise "are
OL,10,Fno longer distant threats," especially
OL,11,Ffor the Pacific.
OL,13,FIf the world continues its path of
OL,14,Fheating to 3 degrees Celsius above pre-
OL,15,Findustrial levels, the Pacific Islands
OL,16,Fcan expect to see at least another 15
OL,17,Fcentimeters of additional sea level
OL,18,Frise by 2050 and more than 30 days of
OL,19,Fcoastal flooding per year, the report
OL,20,Ffound.
