OL,3,C'The ocean is overflowing': UN chief
OL,4,Cissues warning about Pacific sea level
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"This is a region with an average
OL,8,Felevation just 1 to 2 meters above sea
OL,9,Flevel, where around 90% of people live
OL,10,Fwithin 5 kilometers of the coast, and
OL,11,Fwhere half the infrastructure is
OL,12,Fwithin 500 meters of the sea,"
OL,13,FGuterres said.
OL,15,FBoth reports call on global leaders to
OL,16,Fimprove early warning systems for
OL,17,Fvulnerable communities, majorly
OL,18,Fincrease funding for resilience and
OL,19,Fadaptation, and make emission cuts to
OL,20,Fkeep global heating to within 1.5
OL,21,Fdegrees Celsius.
